div.div:
Task-B blocks; hands-off to Plan-B;
custom callback handling:
'booked': advance Task-B to completed state; go to next task
'refused': advance Task-B to cancelled state; make system call ref-svc/bookingRequest(); go to next task
'referred': advance Task-B to completed state; go to next task
timeout (5 mins): log result & display message.
